	  bt_price="500000" maxwt="0" sf="0" fr="0" cr="0" pr="0" lr="0" color="#FFFFFFFF" desc="Though ragged and shabby, guerilla leaders wear their tattered clothes like a badge of honor, a constant reminder of the reasons for rebelling against the Axium Empire. Plus, men with gunz don't need sleeves." />
	<ITEM id="695" name="Leopard Clan Trenchcoat" mesh_name="eq_chest_leopard" totalpoint="0" 
	  type="equip" res_level="25" res_sex="m" weight="14" hp="1" ap="30" iscashitem="false" slot="Chest" 
	  bt_price="500000" maxwt="0" sf="0" fr="0" cr="0" pr="0" lr="0" color="#FFFFFFFF" desc="Members of the Leopard Clan clad themselves in the spots of their namesake to pay tribute to its prowess as a hunter and ability to camouflage. Operating invisibly in both the Empire and the Republic, the clan is known for their savagery and ruthlessness. This coat is a must-have to truly pimp yourself out." />
	<ITEM id="696" name="Imperial Hunter Coat (Men)" mesh_name="eq_chest_primehunter" totalpoint="0" 
