	  bt_price="500000" maxwt="0" sf="0" fr="0" cr="0" pr="0" lr="0" color="#FFFFFFFF" desc="Imperial Hunters are elite bondsmen on direct retainer from the royal family of the Axium Empire. The trademark heavy wool overcoat is paired with a matching cloak and mantle." />
	<ITEM id="697" name="Wayfarer Coat (Men)" mesh_name="eq_chest_vagrant" totalpoint="0" 
	  type="equip" res_level="7" res_sex="m" weight="14" hp="3" ap="20" iscashitem="false" slot="Chest" 
	  bt_price="500000" maxwt="0" sf="0" fr="0" cr="0" pr="0" lr="0" color="#FFFFFFFF" desc="The nomadic tribes of the borderlands live hardscrabble lives. This worn leather duster has been cut short to prevent the flaps from impeding leg movement, while still providing protection from the elements." />

