	  bt_price="500000" maxwt="0" sf="0" fr="0" cr="0" pr="0" lr="0" color="#FFFFFFFF" desc="Though ragged and shabby, guerilla leaders wear their tattered clothes like a badge of honor, a constant reminder of the reasons for rebelling against the Axium Empire. The shin bandage is included to trick enemies into thinking you're weak, giving you the chance to blast their brains onto the brick wall behind them." />
