	  bt_price="500000" maxwt="0" sf="0" fr="0" cr="0" pr="0" lr="0" color="#FFFFFFFF" desc="Members of the Leopard Clan clad themselves in the spots of their namesake to pay tribute to its prowess as a hunter and ability to camouflage. Operating invisibly in both the Empire and the Republic, the clan is known for their savagery and ruthlessness." />
	<ITEM id="1207" name="Imperial Hunter Boots (Women)" mesh_name="eq_feet_primehunter" totalpoint="0" 
